+  finding ¬ß4: Decision 0011, the companion, and the correction ledger all cited fixture
+  CR-9, an example file, and a validator that were never in the tree, and nothing caught
+  it ‚ÄĒ false closure inside a project about false closure. Every entry below must state
+  WHY the path does not resolve; "it is broken" is not a reason.
+external_paths:
